import re
import string
In [27]:
def remove_characters_after_tokenization(tokens):
    pattern = re.compile('[{}]'.format(re.escape(string.punctuation)))
    filtered_tokens = ''.join(filter(None, [pattern.sub('', token) for token in tokens]))
    return filtered_tokens

In [33]:
from contractions import contractions_dict
In [34]:
c_re = re.compile('(%s)' % '|'.join(contractions_dict.keys()))
def expandContractions(text, c_re=c_re):
    def replace(match):
        return contractions_dict[match.group(0)]
    return c_re.sub(replace, text)
In [35]:
Regis_Psve_reviews = [expandContractions(i) for i in Regis_Psve_reviews]
Regis_Ngve_reviews = [expandContractions(i) for i in Regis_Ngve_reviews]
